{"tid":1325037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果香港真係戒嚴....","createTime":"2019-07-16T17:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T18:10:09.000Z","uid":270675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfd22afe355af26ef82c02826b930c1010e1e8c","tid":1325037,"uid":270675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"【戒嚴？斷網？】<br />\n今日有報導指政府正研究分區戒嚴，事關重大，因為特首可引用法例權力對通訊進行管制，甚至最嚴重的&ldquo;斷網&rdquo;。這種做法可能嚴重破壞香港資訊自由的形象，影響互聯網和電訊業運作牽連甚大，&rdquo;斷網&ldquo;一旦發生香港更可能變成非洲獨裁國家的水平。任何影響通訊和電訊的措施必須十分謹慎考量，絕對不能戒嚴和斷網！<br />\n<br />\n相關法例：<br />\n第241章 《緊急情況規例條例》 ─ 第2條 訂立規例的權力<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241!zh-Hant-HK@2018-12-13T00:00:00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap241%21zh-Hant-HK%402018-12-13T00%3A00%3A00&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=ea131074\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap241!zh-Hant-HK@2018-12-13T00:00:00</a><br />\n(1) 在行政長官會同行政會議認為屬 緊急情況或危害公安的情況時 ，行政長官會同行政會議 可訂立任何他認為合乎公眾利益的規例 。<br />\n(2)在不損害第(1)款條文的一般性的原則下，該等規例可就下列事項作出規定<br />\n(a)對刊物、文字、地圖、圖則、照片、 通訊及通訊方法的檢查、管制及壓制 ；<br />\n<br />\n第106章《電訊條例》第13條 在緊急情況下由政府接管電訊電台<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap106!zh-Hant-HK?xpid=ID_1438402544777_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap106%21zh-Hant-HK%3Fxpid%3DID_1438402544777_001&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=08ce12d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap106!zh-Hant-HK?xpid=ID_1438402544777_001</a><br />\n若行政長官認為已發生緊急情況，可簽署手令接管或使用電訊電台，或對其加以控制，手令有效期不多於一週，但可以連續每週發出。條例沒有列明何謂「緊急情況」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSxLuwV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSxLuwV.png&h=85202b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSources:莫乃光"},{"pid":"16e0f8f7ba522cab2a109747fd08a3e54fe6207b","tid":1325037,"uid":54528,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"我好撚驚啊 斷啦<br />\n睇下d股民殺唔殺你全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce85aa076cb06cfca9c4d0e78376ecdb985b9ea1","tid":1325037,"uid":6030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"好驚，係咪要買曬usd即走"},{"pid":"a27a928b3d6e3459dd1dd382cc55f902ce501a93","tid":1325037,"uid":270675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce85aa076cb06cfca9c4d0e78376ecdb985b9ea1","tid":1325037,"uid":6030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:51:35.000Z","msg":"好驚，係咪要買曬usd即走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:53:28.000Z","msg":"用內聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7ab9871ecac0a102620cc259e8d54959a39280","tid":1325037,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到時焦土會好開心，快撚啲戒嚴</span>"},{"pid":"895d858fc5fa48f81e92f45ad69d207a58436148","tid":1325037,"uid":270675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd7ab9871ecac0a102620cc259e8d54959a39280","tid":1325037,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到時焦土會好開心，快撚啲戒嚴</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdkUnZG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdkUnZG.png&h=02ce10ae&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}